  character: 3
  blocks:
  - context: 0
    lines:
    - "Cold is honest. It doesn\u2019t care who you used to be"
    - "Your warmth won\u2019t last long out here!"
  - context: 6
    lines:
    - Healing is patience. Freezing is control!
    - "Breathe slow. Don\u2019t rush on ice!"
  - context: 2
    lines:
    - Find the pickaxe. Some problems require breaking, not solving!
  - context: 7
    lines:
    - The ice cracks from beneath me...
    - I misjudged your will, Exile!
